messages.message:
Build feedback - *Field suggestions*:
• Usually, I'm in Build to optimize existing fields, rarely adding new fields, so having this pop up and get in the way is often an annoyance.
• Now that I recently was working on adding a bunch of fields, I decided to try it; unfortunately, it doesn't seem to do anything. :disappointed:
    ◦ For example, in the pictured pop up (SS1), I tried clicking the purple `Add field` button, but the it simply closed with no change in fields.  Next, I opened it again, and wanted to see what other fields it is suggesting, but upon clicking the right arrow it closed again with no change in fields.
